          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Jacket potato with chilli is a filling weeknight dinner that uses two British staples together. The jacket potato is baked in the usual way while the chilli simmers on the hob. Use the potato-baking time to make the chilli from scratch, or use batch-cooked chilli kept in the fridge.",
              "type": "text"
            }
